'''卡迈什瓦尔·C·瓦利'''（{{lang-en|Kameshwar C. Wali}}，{{bd|1927年|10月15日|}}）是一位[[美国|美国]][[理论物理学|理论物理学]]家
[[雪城大學|雪城大學]][[榮譽退休|榮譽退休]]教授<ref>{{cite web|title=Kameshwar Wali|url=http://www.phy.syr.edu/research/relativity/Wali/index.html|accessdate=1 January 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120528194122/http://www.phy.syr.edu/research/relativity/Wali/index.html|archive-date=2012-05-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，主要研究方向为[[高能物理学|高能物理学]]，特别是基本粒子的对称性和动力学<ref>{{cite web|title=History of Physics Newsletter|url=http://www.aps.org/units/fhp/newsletters/upload/spring06.pdf|accessdate=1 January 2014|archive-date=2012-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120520112811/http://aps.org/units/fhp/newsletters/upload/spring06.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同时他也是一位[[科学史|科学史]]作家<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.worldcat.org/identities/lccn-n86-61294 |title=Chandra : a biography of S. Chandrasekhar |publisher=[[WorldCat|WorldCat]] |date= |accessdate=2014-01-02 |archive-date=2018-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181202155324/http://www.worldcat.org/identities/lccn-n86-61294/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，作品有《孤独的科学之路——[[苏布拉马尼扬·钱德拉塞卡|钱德拉塞卡]]传》（''Chandra: A Biography of S. Chandrasekhar''）等<ref>{{Cite book | url = https://archive.org/details/chandrabiography0000wali | url-access = registration | title = Chandra: A Biography of S. Chandrasekhar | publisher = University of Chicago Press | isbn = 9780226870557 | last1 = Wali | first1 = Kameshwar C | year = 1991}}</ref>。

